    "abstract": "This document describes how the existing IPv6 mechanisms for ping and traceroute can be used in a Segment Routing over IPv6 (SRv6) network. The document also specifies the OAM flag (O-flag) in the Segment Routing Header (SRH) for performing controllable and predictable flow sampling from segment endpoints.  In addition, the document describes how a centralized monitoring system performs a path continuity check between any nodes within an SRv6 domain. ",
